aTaE~ama bilaHomihi", "text_ar": "اـِذَا تَطَعَّمَ بِلَحْمِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", app. meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A dog having his appetite excited by tasting the flesh of the game."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "DawaArK", "text_ar": "ضَوَارٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[is pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "DaArK", "text_ar": "ضَارٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "applied to an irrational animal, and as such] signifies ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Animals accustomed to prey; rapacious,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ravenous, beasts;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and particularly]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lions."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmawaA$iY AlD~aAriyapu", "text_ar": "المَوَاشِى الضَّارِيَةُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The cattle that are in the habit of pasturing upon peoples' seed-produce."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Nh, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayotN DaArK biAll~aHomi", "text_ar": "بَيْتٌ ضَارٍ بِاللَّحْمِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A house,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tent, in which flesh-meat is habitually found so much that its odour remains in it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "siqaA='N DaArK", "text_ar": "سِقَا=ءٌ ضَارٍ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAll~abani", "text_ar": "بِاللَّبَنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", thus correctly, as in the M, but in [some of] the copies of the K"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAls~amoni", "text_ar": "بِالسَّمْنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A skin in which milk is long kept so that its flavour becomes good."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jar~apN DaAriyapN biAlxal~i", "text_ar": "جَرَّةٌ ضَارِيَةٌ بِالخَلِّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": 